{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDA4NTk5Mzg1", "number": 55726, "title": "Allow a number of broadcast transport actions to resolve data streams", "bodyText": "Change TransportBroadcastByNodeAction and TransportBroadcastReplicationAction\nto be able to resolve data streams by default. Implementations can change this ability.\nThis change allows to following APIs to resolve data streams: flush,\nrefresh (already supported data streams), force merge, clear indices cache,\nindices stats, segments, upgrade stats, upgrade, validate query,\nsearchable snapshots stats, clear searchable snapshots cache and\nreload analyzers APIs.\nRelates to #53100", "createdAt": "2020-04-24T14:54:17Z", "url": "https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/pull/55726", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "77aa2362bbb843bce4bc2fceb8b1c65afa2202a6"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-05-11T09:12:08Z", "author": {"login": "martijnvg"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 13, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcaytl_AH2gAyNDA4NTk5Mzg1OjhmZDA0NWEwNTAzMmY3MDM1YTA1Y2VmYzVmOTE3ZTczODMwMzFkNGQ=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcgL5UGgFqTQwODk4OTY0Mw==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "8fd045a05032f7035a05cefc5f917e7383031d4d", "author": {"user": {"login": "martijnvg", "name": "Martijn van Groningen"}}, "url": "https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/commit/8fd045a05032f7035a05cefc5f917e7383031d4d", "committedDate": "2020-04-24T14:53:10Z", "message": "Change the BroadcastRequest default indices options to resolve data stream\n\nBy changing to the default indices options of BroadcastRequest\nthe following apis can resolve data streams: flush,\nrefresh (already supported data streams), force merge, clear indices cache,\nindices stats, segments, upgrade stats, upgrade, validate query,\nsearchable snapshots stats, clear searchable snapshots cache and\nreload analyzers APIs.\n\nThe following APIs extend BroadcastRequest but overwrite default\nindices options and therefor don't yet support data streams:\nrecovery api\n\nThis change also adds `strictIncludeDataStreamsExpand()` to `IndicesOptions`\nclass. (an alternative to `strictExpand()`) This is because\n`InternalClusterInfoService` overwrites the default indices options\nfor the indices stats call.\n\nRelates to #53100"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "bbe6a32c66f1805c922529399900af2022b72a3e", "author": {"user": {"login": "martijnvg", "name": "Martijn van Groningen"}}, "url": "https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/commit/bbe6a32c66f1805c922529399900af2022b72a3e", "committedDate": "2020-04-24T14:55:13Z", "message": "renamed test"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "9a7406c4ad09326083e596de860256040d6f7c53", "author": {"user": {"login": "martijnvg", "name": "Martijn van Groningen"}}, "url": "https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/commit/9a7406c4ad09326083e596de860256040d6f7c53", "committedDate": "2020-04-24T15:05:31Z", "message": "fixed assertion"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "6eee5add437a030642298ba787a619a6bbaa09b7", "author": {"user": {"login": "martijnvg", "name": "Martijn van Groningen"}}, "url": "https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/commit/6eee5add437a030642298ba787a619a6bbaa09b7", "committedDate": "2020-04-24T16:10:39Z", "message": "adjusted tests"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "61b81cafc8aa3ed8c5b5d44b513119a255ed8ddb", "author": {"user": {"login": "martijnvg", "name": "Martijn van Groningen"}}, "url": "https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/commit/61b81cafc8aa3ed8c5b5d44b513119a255ed8ddb", "committedDate": "2020-04-24T17:41:24Z", "message": "fixed typo"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NDAwMjgyMjcw", "url": "https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/pull/55726#pullrequestreview-400282270", "createdAt": "2020-04-24T21:29:38Z", "co